      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model and Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model are standard choices for this application. Model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2 Gradation 1; no formal sensitivity to alternative model forms was conducted."
    },
    {
